    "For this, we generate training datasets of varying sizes, by randomly sampling examples from the original dataset across a range from 5% to 100%.",
    "Figure 8 illustrates that post-hoc verification of VERIFINER leads to notable enhancements in the performance of both BioBERT and ConNER across all low-resource scenarios examined in both datasets.",
